OL,3,CBorn to run: Chalmers reclaims British
OL,4,Ctitle and welcomes son in same week
OL,6,FGuernsey's Alastair Chalmers won back
OL,7,Fhis British 400m hurdles title on
OL,8,FSunday, in the same week that he
OL,9,Fwelcomed his newborn son.
OL,11,FThe 26-year-old stormed to victory,
OL,12,Fbeating Joshua Faulds into silver by
OL,13,F0.32 seconds. The victory saw him
OL,14,Freclaim the British Champion crown
OL,15,Fthat he lost to Tyri Donovan last
OL,16,Fyear. It is his sixth national title.
OL,18,FThe runner's fiancee, Ellie Bell, gave
OL,19,Fbirth on Tuesday morning, just five
OL,20,Fdays before this year's 400m hurdle
OL,21,Ffinal.
