OL,3,CBorn to run: Chalmers reclaims British
OL,4,Ctitle and welcomes son in same week
OL,6,FBy Sunday, Chalmers was bringing baby
OL,7,FRobert onto the track after winning
OL,8,Fgold.
OL,10,FHe told ITV News that the week was "an
OL,11,Fabsolute blessing and a surreal
OL,12,Fexperience".
OL,14,F"To win a gold medal for him, on
OL,15,FFather's Day, it was written in the
OL,16,Fstars that that was going to happen."
