FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1782169392
OL,3,CBorn to run: Chalmers reclaims British
OL,4,Ctitle and welcomes son in same week
OL,6,FThe sportsman won Guernsey's first-
OL,7,Fever athletics medal in the
OL,8,FCommonwealth Games in 2022 and hopes
OL,9,Fto repeat his success in Glasgow next
OL,10,Fmonth.
OL,12,F"I'm wanting to go and win a medal at
OL,13,Fthe Commonwealth and the Europeans",
OL,14,Fhe told ITV News. "That's the most
OL,15,Fimportant thing."
OL,17,FThe Commonwealth Games start on 23
OL,18,FJuly and the 400m final will take
OL,19,Fplace on the evening of 31 July.
